sequenceDiagram
  %% 完成形の1回の memory query シーケンス図: 経路選択から引用付き回答または棄権までを見る

  actor User as 人 / AI agent
  participant RX as research_x API
  participant Lens as SearchLens
  participant Route as ObjectiveRoutePolicy / Route Portfolio
  participant Guard as ProviderApiBudgetGuard
  participant Evidence as Source Bundle / Context / Citation
  participant Authority as AnswerAuthorityGatekeeper
  participant Boundary as Answer Boundary
  participant Trace as 監査と評価

  User->>RX: query / objective / context budget
  RX->>Trace: sidecar trace を開始する
  RX->>Lens: 関心・重み・探索姿勢を確認する
  Lens->>Route: 目的に合う候補経路を選ぶ

  opt provider-backed route
    Route->>Guard: 予算と停止条件を確認する
    Guard-->>Route: provider candidates or provider_gated skip
  end

  Route->>Evidence: 候補を source bundle / context chunk / citation へ復元する
  Evidence->>Authority: claim support を確認する
  Authority->>Boundary: answer support または停止理由
  Boundary->>Trace: 品質と停止理由を保存する

  alt 回答できる
    Boundary-->>RX: answer with citations
    RX-->>User: 引用付き回答
  else 回答すべきでない
    Boundary-->>RX: abstain / needs_review / hypothesis_only / provider_gated
    RX-->>User: 理由つきで返す
  end
